The '''Compulsory Purchase Act 1965''' ([http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ukpga/1965/56/contents c 56]) is an [[Act of Parliament]] of the [[United Kingdom]], which concerns [[English land law]] and [[Compulsory purchase in England and Wales|compulsory purchase]].

==Contents==
The Act sets conditions for a compulsory purchase to be made.

